and you'd do it again. right?

206
00:10:52.129 --> 00:10:53.129
Wouldn't you?

207
00:10:55.263 --> 00:10:56.263
Yeah. [CHUCKLES] Okay.

208
00:10:56.438 --> 00:10:57.807
