226
00:11:58.195 --> 00:12:00.067
You know. if you're not going
to call me Dad.

227
00:12:00.154 --> 00:12:01.155
you could at least...

228
00:12:01.242 --> 00:12:02.373
[MUSIC CONCLUDES]

229
00:12:02.460 --> 00:12:04.593
DANIEL: You could at least
call me Danny.

230
00:12:05.463 --> 00:12:06.856
