231
00:12:06.943 --> 00:12:10.207
[UPBEAT MUSIC
PLAYING OVER RADIO]

232
00:12:10.338 --> 00:12:11.208
[INDISTINCT CHATTER]

233
00:12:11.295 --> 00:12:13.297
ALEX: Thank you.
DANIEL: Thanks.

234
00:12:16.605 --> 00:12:19.564
It seems like there's a dress
code. If you're too embarrassed

235
00:12:19.651 --> 00:12:21.629
