in the truck. you know?

236
00:12:21.653 --> 00:12:23.917
No. I wanna go
to the parents thing.

237
00:12:24.700 --> 00:12:26.136
See what this place
is all about.

238
00:12:26.310 --> 00:12:27.310
Okay.

239
00:12:27.529 --> 00:12:29.183
Just so you know.
all you have to do is

240
00:12:29.270 --> 00:12:30.750
